  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to estimate the impact of the implication of a Mobile Team of
      Palliative Care (EMSP) on the palliative strategy in the units with concerned patients. The
      Mobile Team of Palliative of Foch hospital Care was created in March, 2011.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
